338
00:24:54,040 --> 00:24:55,420
How could the Tonoji family

339
00:24:55,680 --> 00:24:57,460
be so foolish?

340
00:24:59,630 --> 00:25:00,570
Major General,

341
00:25:02,040 --> 00:25:05,220
