342
00:25:05,240 --> 00:25:08,700
by an anti-Japanese operative, right?

343
00:25:13,720 --> 00:25:15,740
Lin Megumi.

344
00:25:16,720 --> 00:25:17,420
Major General,

345
00:25:18,680 --> 00:25:20,180
right now the Tonoji family members

346
00:25:20,200 --> 00:25:21,220
